Bongo stars Diamond Platnumz and Juma Jux are among artistes who have stood with Kenyans over Tuesday's terror attack. Diamond: "Maombi yangu yapo kwenu KENYA…Poleni sana na Inshaallah Mwenyezi Mungu atawasimamia." Jux: "Praying for Kenya." Harmonize wrote: "Poleni sana, Ndugu zangu Mitihani huletwa na Mungu na kwa uwezo wake basi litapita." Chameleon: "Pole pole pole sana. I stand with you, my brothers and sisters. Chris Shalom: "Evil will not prevail in Kenya! Kenya is stronger, greater, peaceful, more fruitful and flourishing in Jesus name! Tarrus Riley: "Protect yuh People Jah Jah Guide n Protect Kenya."